node_modules
# Anchor with a leading slash so we only exclude the production output
# directory at the app root (`apps/learn-card-app/build/`), not every
# directory named `build` in the tree. The Pathways module has a
# `src/pages/pathways/build/` subtree (Build mode) that Rollup needs;
# without the anchor, the Docker image is assembled without it and
# `PathwaysShell.tsx`'s dynamic import of `./build/BuildMode` fails.
/build
